We recommended the Municipal Mayor to:

1. Direct the Municipal Health Officer to prepare and submit the utilization report with complete supporting documents to the accounting office;

2. Enforce measures such as “No utilization report No requisition” policy on supplies for all departments; 

3. Require the Inventory Committee to regularly conduct physical count of unused supplies as prescribed in Section 124 - Volume I of NGAS Manual and submit report to the office of COA; and 

