Recommendations:

 We recommended that the Municipal Mayor:

1.  Assess the manner of implementing 20% development fund through downloading of funds to the barangay. The capacity and resources of the barangay should be considered in this undertaking to ensure efficiency in the implementation of development projects in their level;

2.   Instruct the Heads of Implementing Offices to review budget allocation of identified development projects to ensure full implementation during the year;

3.   Direct the General Services Office (GSO) or the Information Technology (IT) unit to provide assistance to barangays who cannot access the PhilGEPS to commence the procurement process of pending projects; and 

4.   Instruct the Municipal Engineer to require the barangays to submit documents as bases in downloading to start off 2018 projects.

We recommended that the Management

(a) continue being compliant with the Ecological Solid Waste Management Act of 2000; 

(b) continue to assist the 10 remaining barangays in the establishment of their MRF and; 

(c) keep on exerting its best efforts on assisting the Department of Natural Resource and other concern agencies on the Implementation of rehabilitation, restoration, and conservation of the Manila Bay.

